## SECURITY REMINDERS

```
❌ NEVER DO THIS:
subprocess.run(f'command {user_input}', shell=True)

✅ DO THIS:
subprocess.run(['command', user_input])

❌ NEVER DO THIS:
subprocess.run('rm -rf / ' + dir, shell=True)

✅ DO THIS:
subprocess.run(['rm', '-rf', dir])
```

