## COMMON MISTAKES

```python
# ❌ WRONG: Bytes vs strings
result = subprocess.run(['ls'], capture_output=True)
print(result.stdout)  # b'output\n' - bytes!

# ✅ RIGHT: Use text=True
result = subprocess.run(['ls'], capture_output=True, text=True)
print(result.stdout)  # 'output\n' - string

# ❌ WRONG: Ignoring timeout
result = subprocess.run(['sleep', '100'])  # Hangs forever!

# ✅ RIGHT: Always set timeout
result = subprocess.run(['sleep', '100'], timeout=5)

# ❌ WRONG: Shell injection
target = user_input
subprocess.run(f'ping {target}', shell=True)

# ✅ RIGHT: Safe list format
subprocess.run(['ping', '-c', '4', target])
```

